{"word":"πρωΐ","slug":"πρωΐ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πρωΐ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:πρό\">πρό</a></el> (marker of precedence) and <el>πρῴην</el> (also <el>πρώην</el>) ‘recently’] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adv.\">adv.</a> <b>early (in the morning)<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> without indication of specific time <b><a href='B:470 16:3'>Mt 16:3</a>; <a href='B:470 20:1'>20:1</a>; <a href='B:470 21:18'>21:18</a>; <a href='B:480 1:35'>Mk 1:35</a>; <a href='B:480 11:20'>11:20</a>; <a href='B:480 15:1'>15:1</a>; <a href='B:480 16:2'>16:2</a>, <a href='B:480 16:9'>9</a>; <a href='B:500 18:28'>J 18:28</a>; <a href='B:500 20:1'>20:1</a>; <a href='B:510 28:23'>Ac 28:23</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> according to Roman reckoning, as the fourth watch of the night, <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ fr.\">fr.</a> 3 to 6 <b><a href='B:480 13:35'>Mk 13:35</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πρύμνα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πρωΐα\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}